lead_paragraph: The ACT Brumbies and Stormers made statements, there were defeats for last year's finalists but biggest impact on the balance of power in Super Rugby from the opening weekend of the new season may be the arrival of Argentina's Jaguares.

headline.print_headline: Jaguares Shine as Super Rugby Returns With a Bang
headline.main: Jaguares Shine as Super Rugby Returns With a Bang
